Ndini ingwe.

0:00:35.560,0:00:36.900
Iwe unorevei kana uchiti uri ingwe?

0:00:36.900,0:00:41.980
Ndinongoda zvishoma. Kana akakwanisa kuteerera - hapana chinetso.

