0:02:39.140,0:02:42.320
Ndakamutevera nhano ne nhano.

0:02:42.320,0:02:45.320
Ndakamuyamwisa nekumupa zvose.

0:02:45.320,0:02:52.760
Zvakaitika sei, kuti panguva yekundibhadhara, akatendeukira kuna Mwari wandisingazivi?

0:02:52.760,0:02:54.220
Ndakamubvumira.

0:02:54.220,0:02:56.420
Zvino - hapana.

0:02:56.420,0:03:00.740
Haana kunyange imba. Ndinoreva imba.

