0:04:37.760,0:04:42.580
Apo nguva yakakwana, ndakakonzera matambudziko muchechi.

0:04:42.580,0:04:47.420
Ndakaisa mhaka; zvose zvaiva zvenhema.

0:04:47.420,0:04:53.140
Ndakaita kuti vanhu vamuvenge pasina chikonzero.

0:04:53.140,0:04:56.160
Chii chakaitika kuhushumiri hwake zvino?

0:04:56.160,0:04:57.600
Ushumiri?

